  <name>OLED Saver</name>
  
  <summary>Screen saver for OLED displays</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>OLED-Saver is a small tool that prevents your device from entering standby mode. It displays a completely black screen to protect the OLED display from potential burn-in effects. The application takes into account the desktop environments Gnome, KDE, and XFCE, and adjusts the energy-saving behavior accordingly.</p>
